4229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an interview\", \"from\": 329, \"to\": 341}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday's opening ceremony\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 429}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris 2024 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 433, \"to\": 461}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I thought that the opening ceremony was a disgrace, actually,\\\"said Trump.\", \"from\": 464, \"to\": 538, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 500}, {\"ngram\": \"a disgrace\", \"from\": 505, \"to\": 515}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I thought it was a disgrace.\\\"\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 569, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a disgrace\", \"from\": 557, \"to\": 567}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He appeared to be referring to a scene in which a group of drag artists and dancers were positioned behind a long table, causing some to compare it to Leonardo DaVinci's \\\"The Last Supper,\\\" a Rennaissance painting that depicts Jesus Christ with his Twelve Apostles.\", \"from\": 571, \"to\": 835, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 722, \"end\": 730, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7853231103233444e-18, \"text\": \"Leonardo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}, {\"begin\": 731, \"end\": 738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1114831048247576e-23, \"text\": \"DaVinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}, {\"begin\": 797, \"end\": 809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9996859167107157, \"rank\": 0.0003141819686623471, \"text\": \"Jesus Christ\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627