o\": 2336}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She has been targeted with death, torture and rape, and has also been the target of numerous anti-Semitic, homophobic, sexist and grossophobic insults,\\\" her attorney, Audrey Msellati, wrote in aletter posted on Butch's Instagram.\", \"from\": 2355, \"to\": 2585, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2449, \"end\": 2461, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antisemitism\", \"score\": 0.9999999998744897, \"rank\": 1.255052319735692e-10, \"text\": \"anti-Semitic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antisemitism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antisemitism\"}, {\"begin\": 2523, \"end\": 2529, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Audrey_Horne\", \"score\": 0.717568179778755, \"rank\": 0.39359579727741584, \"text\": \"Audrey\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Audrey_Horne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Audrey_Horne\"}, {\"begin\": 2575, \"end\": 2584, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.933950782841349e-22, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"death\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2388}, {\"ngram\": \"torture\", \"from\": 2390, \"to\": 2397}, {\"ngram\": \"rape\", \"from\": 2402, \"to\": 2406}, {\"ngram\": \"the target\", \"from\": 2426, \"to\": 2436}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\" her attorney\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2521}, {\"ngram\": \"aletter\", \"from\": 2549, \"to\": 2556}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She is today filing several complaints against these acts, whether committed by French nationals or foreigners, and intends to prosecute anyone who tries to intimidate her in the future.\\\"\", \"from\": 2586, \"to\": 2774, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2667, \"end\": 2673, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0